name: absolute
description: Applies position: absolute to the component.

name: bottom
description: Aligns the component towards the bottom.

name: collapse
description: Puts the toolbar into a collapsed state reducing its maximum width.

name: color
description: Applies specified color to the control - it can be the name of material color (for example success or purple) or css color (#033 or rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5)). You can find list of built in classes on the colors page.

name: dark
description: Applies the dark theme variant to the component. You can find more information on the Material Design documentation for dark themes.

name: dense
description: Reduces the height of the toolbar content to 48px (96px when using the prominent prop).

name: elevation
description: Designates an elevation applied to the component between 0 and 24. You can find more information on the elevation page.

name: extended
description: Use this prop to increase the height of the toolbar without using the extension slot for adding content. May be used in conjunction with the extension-height prop, and any of the other props that affect the height of the toolbar, e.g. prominent, dense, etc., WITH THE EXCEPTION of height.

name: extension-height
description: Specify an explicit height for the extension slot.

name: flat
description: Removes the toolbar's box-shadow.

name: floating
description: Applies display: inline-flex to the component.

name: height
description: Designates a specific height for the toolbar. Overrides the heights imposed by other props, e.g. prominent, dense, extended, etc.

name: light
description: Applies the light theme variant to the component.

name: max-height
description: Sets the maximum height for the component.

name: max-width
description: Sets the maximum width for the component.

name: min-height
description: Sets the minimum height for the component.

name: min-width
description: Sets the minimum width for the component.

name: prominent
description: Increases the height of the toolbar content to 128px.

name: short
description: Reduce the height of the toolbar content to 56px (112px when using the prominent prop).

name: src
description: Specifies a v-img as the component's background.

name: tag
description: Specify a custom tag used on the root element.

name: tile
description: Removes the component's border-radius.

name: width
description: Sets the width for the component.
